chart_description: This chart displays the number of seconds since 1970 of the last garbage collection performed by the Go memory manager in the aws-cluster-autoscaler infrastructure.

dimension_descriptions.go_memstats_last_gc_time_seconds: The number of seconds since 1970 of the last garbage collection. This dimension provides insight into the frequency of garbage collection performed by the Go memory manager in the aws-cluster-autoscaler infrastructure.
